rows.label: tlk42300021_02_msg0002

anyone has been in or out, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_02_msg0003

good use of it, is it, mo?

rows.label: tlk42300021_02_msg0004

This time, I'll make my business
a success in Torigo, mo!
